Iterable<org.graphstream.graph.Node>, org.graphstream.graph.Element, org.graphstream.graph.Graph, org.graphstream.graph.Structure, org.graphstream.stream.AttributeSink, org.graphstream.stream.ElementSink, org.graphstream.stream.Pipe, org.graphstream.stream.Replayable, org.graphstream.stream.Sink, org.graphstream.stream.Source, IPetrinetView
public class GraphStreamPetrinet extends org.graphstream.graph.implementations.MultiGraph implements IPetrinetView
The class is an implementation of the interface IPetrinetView using the GraphStream library (it derives from MultiGraph) to display a Petri net graph. It is part of the applications view.
